evidence that wrongdoing occurred 
many facts in the case are not in dispute committee chairman 
howell t heflin dala and vice chairman warren b rudman 
rnh said durenbergers motivations could play a major role in 
determining guilt or innocence 
following the hearings the panel of three republicans and three 
