the committee will serve as prosecutor jim hamilton a former 
counsel to the senate watergate committee will represent 
durenberger neither is a stranger to the ethics committee 
bennett played the role of prosecutor in 1981 in the case of 
former sen harrison a williams jr dnj when the committee 
last held triallike proceedings to determine ethical wrongdoing 
the committee began its investigation after williams already had 
been convicted in federal court on nine bribery and conspiracy 
counts in the abscam political corruption scandal bennett 
recommended expulsion and the full senate was about to oust williams 
