durenbergers troubles its between the senator and his 
colleagues at this point said anita dunn spokeswoman for the 
democratic senatorial campaign committee 
durenbergers friends in the senate are defending him 
you would have a lot of congressmen and senators who would fail 
to shine under the microscope said sen don nickles rokla 
